text: Kiss Me Once is the twelfth studio album by Australian singer Kylie Minogue. It was released worldwide on 14 March 2014 by Parlophone Records, and is her first studio album since Aphrodite (2010). The album contains two singles, "Into the Blue" and "I Was Gonna Cancel". ==Track listing== == Other websites == *Official website of Kylie Minogue Category:2014 albums Category:Kylie Minogue albums Category:Dance-pop albums
